":"=✅ Streamline a multi-step process with HTTP / REST API and Airtable and  — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftTeams","typeVersion":2,"position":[3618,400],"id":"8dcb8b04-37ca-4d4e-9e8f-27ca900a5cd2","name":"Send Summary to Microsoft Teams","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Map to Canonical Schema","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"ab9deba7-5c8f-32f2-9a0a-8b304f6bc2bc","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Map to Canonical Schema\n\nShapes the item: writes `jobId`, `kind`, `payload`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Route by Event Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"6e29d4d1-c45e-80b6-dcf0-801a668c2604","name":"Note: Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: job.start, job.done + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'job.start' → Airtable · ②→ Handle 'job.done' → Forward API · ③→ Log Unrecognized Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"c6b90716-61a4-dd6e-34c1-c4d470b3eaa9","name":"Note: Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'job.start' → Airtable\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,250],"id":"214df2b0-7b8c-6dd5-a2b2-d5fef488a5c1","name":"Note: Handle 'job.start' → Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'job.done' → Forward API\n\nPOST https://api.example.com/v1/jobs — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,760],"id":"b97b9762-e272-0b36-f0eb-a2ff72c42356","name":"Note: Handle 'job.done' → Forward API"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Log Unrecognized Kind\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1270],"id":"8cd1ac1f-bf0d-cc6d-6495-bd0d7365ca86","name":"Note: Log Unrecognized Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Consolidate Handling\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"b05a5335-3537-0d6d-c328-03534f6ea464","name":"Note: Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"a49eae61-833a-ee6d-98ab-f3fe2dfbf70e","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Send Summary to Microsoft Teams","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"f5be555b-8cd6-f554-cb40-791c4eb82487","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Microsoft Teams\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"7b390100-813f-142d-6157-c8e09bd44336","name":"Note: Send Summary to Microsoft Teams"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Streamline a multi-step process with HTTP / REST API and Airtable and log the results\n\n**Pattern:** Workflow Automation · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nStreamline a multi-step process with HTTP / REST API and Airtable and log the results. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual utilities is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Map to Canonical Schema → Route by Event Kind → Handle 'job.start' → Airtable → Consolidate Handling → Stamp Processing Time → Save Execution Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to workflow automation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating utilities in productivity\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Improves response time\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Airtable PAT; Microsoft OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"06518156-af74-25d6-e6c7-fd61cde5067b","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your utilities process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"1dcf8e42-bad5-6ff8-62c0-f8a87330b7b7","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Map to Canonical Schema","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Map to Canonical Schema":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Event Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Event Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Handle 'job.start' → Airtable","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Handle 'job.done' → Forward API","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Log Unrecognized Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'job.start' → Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'job.done' → Forward API":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Log Unrecognized Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":2}]]},"Consolidate Handling":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Microsoft Teams","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"def073f8-9e03-42b9-a15c-94c717f77e6c","id":"FDX06259"}